    {
      "name": "Fog Cloud",
      "type": "spell",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create a 20-foot-radius sphere of fog centered on a point within range. The sphere spreads around corners, and its area is <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/book.html#PHB,8,vision%20and%20light,0\"   >heavily obscured</a>. It lasts for the duration or until a wind of moderate or greater speed (at least 10 miles per hour) disperses it.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6237\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the radius of the fog increases by 20 feet for each slot level above 1st.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
