    {
      "name": "Innate Spellcasting",
      "type": "feat",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6239\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Innate Spellcasting.</span></span> <p>The triton's spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">15</span>, [[/r 1d20+7]] (+7) to hit with spell attacks). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>At will: @spell[ray of frost] (see \"Actions\" below)</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>2/day: @spell[cone of cold]</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>1/day each: @spell[fog cloud], @spell[gust of wind], @spell[wind wall]</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
